HEADWORD: magnetic equator
<hw>magnetic equator</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An imaginary line
paralleling the equator where a magnetic needle has no dip, the dipping
needle being horizontal; called also <altname>aclinic
line</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

